&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/@bug_elseif" target="_blank"&gt;Inscreva-se!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Videos"></category><category term="Conteudo"></category></entry><entry><title>O que é hacktoberfest</title><link href="https://bugelseif.github.io/website/o-que-e-hacktoberfest.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2022-10-08T00:00:00-03:00</published><updated>2022-10-08T00:00:00-03:00</updated><author><name>Bruna Ferreira</name></author><id>tag:bugelseif.github.io,2022-10-08:/website/o-que-e-hacktoberfest.html</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Em 2022 participei pela segunda vez da Hacktoberfest, fiz essa palestra mostrando como participar do evento. Junto da &lt;a href="https://feministech.com.br/" target="_blank"&gt;Feministech&lt;/a&gt; também abordamos temas como Git, Github e Open Source.&lt;/p&gt;
